        <ul class="about-bullets" data-stagger>
          <li data-stagger-item><strong>One brain, one builder.</strong> No agency middlemen.</li>
          <li data-stagger-item><strong>Shipped:</strong> a CBSE school, a 600K YouTuber, a Himachal tour op, a moto-apparel brand, a Himalayan booking platform.</li>
          <li data-stagger-item><strong>WhatsApp reply in 1 hour</strong> (9 AM–9 PM). GST invoice. Day-5 refund.</li>
